2. Data structure - List
see more: docs.python.org

num_list = [1,2,3,4,5]
num_list[0] = 1
num__list[-1] = 5
num_list.append(6)
num_list => [1,2,3,4,5,6]
add_list = [7,8]
num_list.extend(add_list)
num_list => [1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8]
